_chemical_name_common            
;
4,11-Difluoro-quinacridone
Model A from Rietveld refinement
Attention! This is a wrong structural model, which fits well 
to the powder data, fits well to the pair-distribution function,
behaves well in lattice-energy minimisations, and agrees with
solid-state NMR data.
Further discussion see publication.
;
